Package com.facebook.buck.core.sourcepath.resolver

Class SourcePathResolverAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.core.sourcepath.resolver.SourcePathResolverAdapter
  • public class SourcePathResolverAdapter
extends Object
    Adapter that makes SourcePathResolver compatible with client code that assumes each SourcePath resolves to only one Path.

    See also AbstractSourcePathResolver.
